That's what I heard.

195
00:13:04,305 --> 00:13:05,225
No way.

196
00:13:05,305 --> 00:13:08,584
I heard that Feng is seriously
obsessed with cleanliness.

197
00:13:08,585 --> 00:13:11,305
He will only swim in private pools.

198
00:13:11,905 --> 00:13:13,304
That's an idol for you.

199
00:13:13,305 --> 00:13:16,785
He even takes the finest details
so seriously.

200
00:13:17,225 --> 00:13:18,465
Let's go.

201
00:13:41,305 --> 00:13:42,345
Hey.

202
00:13:42,425 --> 00:13:44,635
