213
00:14:33,385 --> 00:14:34,665
Lin Yiyang.

214
00:14:35,105 --> 00:14:41,015
If you want to learn how to swim,
you've got to overcome your fear of water.

215
00:14:41,745 --> 00:14:43,184
Qingqing, are you okay?

216
00:14:43,185 --> 00:14:46,225
Fangfang, you scared me!

217
00:14:51,065 --> 00:14:52,465
Let's be friends.

218
00:14:58,905 --> 00:15:00,504
