I saw it myself.

234
00:15:41,785 --> 00:15:42,784
I saw it myself, too.

235
00:15:42,785 --> 00:15:45,355
You just said you heard about it.

236
00:15:46,185 --> 00:15:49,264
Everyone knows that Lin Yiyang
is the big bully on campus.

237
00:15:49,265 --> 00:15:51,384
