258
00:17:00,945 --> 00:17:02,725
I'll keep it for now.

259
00:17:05,105 --> 00:17:07,624
<i>My errands service has opened
for business for a week</i>

260
00:17:07,625 --> 00:17:10,264
<i>and it didn't even reach 100,000 yuan.</i>

261
00:17:10,265 --> 00:17:12,944
<i>I'm due to pay him by tomorrow the latest.</i>

262
00:17:12,945 --> 00:17:15,624
<i>And I haven't even
joined the Student Council.</i>

263
00:17:15,625 --> 00:17:23,064
<i>Am I going to be kicked out of college
just because I don't have the money?</i>

264
00:17:23,065 --> 00:17:25,145
DANIEL, CELEBRITY BROKER

265
00:17:26,825 --> 00:17:29,744
Mr. Zhou, I've paid up
all the compensation.

266
00:17:29,745 --> 00:17:32,904
-Don't break the rules next time.
-Yes, sir.

267
00:17:32,905 --> 00:17:35,104
I'll follow what you told me.

268
00:17:35,105 --> 00:17:37,315
May I go back to class now?

269
00:17:37,785 --> 00:17:38,875
See you, sir.

270
00:17:41,025 --> 00:17:44,815
-What are you doing here?
-Mind your own business.

271
00:17:45,265 --> 00:17:46,185
Hey.

272
00:17:47,025 --> 00:17:49,945
I heard you're now Feng's assistant.

273
00:17:51,425 --> 00:17:53,144
Boy, the word got out fast.

274
00:17:53,145 --> 00:17:55,944
That's right, I'm Feng's new assistant.

275
00:17:55,945 --> 00:17:58,905
I'm his private, personal assistant.

276
00:17:59,705 --> 00:18:03,135
Stop putting up an act.
I know that already.

277
00:18:03,465 --> 00:18:06,345
But you're only an assistant by name.

278
00:18:07,265 --> 00:18:09,225
That's what others think.

279
00:18:09,305 --> 00:18:12,375
Now, I'm not only Situ Feng's deskmate.

280
00:18:12,465 --> 00:18:14,235
I'm now his assistant.

281
00:18:14,385 --> 00:18:17,425
His private, personal assistant.

282
00:18:17,705 --> 00:18:18,745
And you.

283
00:18:19,225 --> 00:18:21,345
You're none of that.

284
00:18:27,625 --> 00:18:31,144
Did Qingqing really agree
to be your assistant?

285
00:18:31,145 --> 00:18:32,344
That crazy bitch.

286
00:18:32,345 --> 00:18:36,584
She said she wasn't a fan of mine,
yet she bought a lot of tickets.

287
00:18:36,585 --> 00:18:38,584
I think you should be more careful.

288
00:18:38,585 --> 00:18:42,704
You once said, whoever crosses you,
it's not going to end well for them.

289
00:18:42,705 --> 00:18:46,755
I see that things haven't been great
for you lately.

290
00:18:49,665 --> 00:18:51,825
This is the last one.

291
00:18:51,905 --> 00:18:53,905
Thanks for coming.

292
00:18:54,425 --> 00:18:56,145
-Bye.
-Bye.

293
00:18:59,465 --> 00:19:00,545
Chen Qingqing.

294
00:19:00,785 --> 00:19:01,984
What are you doing?

295
00:19:01,985 --> 00:19:05,304
I didn't think your tickets
would sell so well.

296
00:19:05,305 --> 00:19:08,704
All I did was post it
on the college's discussion forum

297
00:19:08,705 --> 00:19:10,504
and everyone started asking
about the cost.

298
00:19:10,505 --> 00:19:12,544
So I earned a lot
by reselling the tickets.

299
00:19:12,545 --> 00:19:14,235
-Qingqing, you--
-Hey.

300
00:19:16,985 --> 00:19:19,104
You didn't like her errands service,
right?

301
00:19:19,105 --> 00:19:21,624
She'll stop the service
after she gets the money she needs.

302
00:19:21,625 --> 00:19:23,635
Just like what you wanted.

303
00:19:24,265 --> 00:19:26,345
What did you say about me?

304
00:19:26,705 --> 00:19:27,705
Nothing.

305
00:19:30,145 --> 00:19:33,435
QINGQING'S ERRANDS SERVICE
OPEN FOR BUSINESS

306
00:19:44,825 --> 00:19:47,425
Come on!

307
00:19:47,665 --> 00:19:52,065
Golden VIP seats up for rent!

308
00:19:52,705 --> 00:19:54,104
Right next to His Highness!

309
00:19:54,105 --> 00:19:55,944
Nothing is stopping you to be with him.

310
00:19:55,945 --> 00:19:59,224
Sometimes you may
run into him by accident.

311
00:19:59,225 --> 00:20:02,265
It's a real face-to-face contact!

312
00:20:02,505 --> 00:20:05,904
Limited seats available.
Hurry while stocks last!

313
00:20:05,905 --> 00:20:07,224
SEAT FOR RENT - HIS HIGHNESS

314
00:20:07,225 --> 00:20:10,464
Qingqing, don't you have
enough money already?

315
00:20:10,465 --> 00:20:13,064
Even so, I can still earn more, right?

316
00:20:13,065 --> 00:20:14,944
Besides, I've thought about it.

317
00:20:14,945 --> 00:20:18,184
Neither of us want to share the same desk
with each other.

318
00:20:18,185 --> 00:20:21,445
So instead, why don't I rent out my seat?

319
00:20:21,545 --> 00:20:26,945
It just happens that I can help
those pure-hearted girls that like you.

320
00:20:28,505 --> 00:20:30,704
Hey! What the hell, Situ Feng?

321
00:20:30,705 --> 00:20:34,185
Your errands service
should stop right now!

322
00:20:35,745 --> 00:20:37,025
You can go now.

323
00:20:37,225 --> 00:20:39,025
Hey, don't go!

324
00:20:40,505 --> 00:20:43,135
Situ Feng, why are you doing this?

325
00:20:43,145 --> 00:20:45,275
Because you're my assistant.

326
00:20:45,345 --> 00:20:50,375
Once you signed up to be my assistant,
if you breach the contract,

327
00:20:50,665 --> 00:20:56,315
you'll need to compensate me more
than that painting is going to cost you.

328
00:20:56,465 --> 00:20:57,385
Fine.

329
00:20:57,465 --> 00:21:00,185
I am your assistant, Situ Feng.

330
00:21:00,265 --> 00:21:03,425
Chen Qingqing is a woman of her word.

331
00:21:03,985 --> 00:21:07,285
All right, my assistant.
Get me some water.

332
00:21:09,345 --> 00:21:10,185
Go!

333
00:21:15,665 --> 00:21:17,144
Hey, you spilled the water!

334
00:21:17,145 --> 00:21:19,475
Aren't you going to drink it?

335
00:21:20,945 --> 00:21:27,215
Hey, cold water? How many times do I have
to tell you? I have a sensitive stomach!

336
00:21:32,265 --> 00:21:33,864
Hey, the water is so hot!

337
00:21:33,865 --> 00:21:37,795
Do you want me to burn my tongue?
Get another one.

338
00:21:48,185 --> 00:21:52,655
Your gym teacher has an emergency.
We'll have math instead.

339
00:21:53,145 --> 00:21:54,775
Distribute the papers.

340
00:22:00,505 --> 00:22:02,775
Let's see how badly you did.

341
00:22:02,945 --> 00:22:04,385
Situ Feng.

342
00:22:05,465 --> 00:22:07,225
I'm warning you.

343
00:22:07,785 --> 00:22:11,384
You'd better not leave anything
I can use against you.

344
00:22:11,385 --> 00:22:13,345
If not...

345
00:22:17,905 --> 00:22:19,145
Situ Feng.

346
00:22:19,705 --> 00:22:22,064
Do you know that you scored
the lowest in your class?

347
00:22:22,065 --> 00:22:25,144
And you've lowered the class average
by three points.

348
00:22:25,145 --> 00:22:27,065
When I call your names,

349
00:22:27,545 --> 00:22:30,344
you'll be paired up into study groups.

350
00:22:30,345 --> 00:22:31,545
Group One.

351
00:22:32,505 --> 00:22:34,705
Chen Qingqing, Situ Feng.

352
00:22:35,945 --> 00:22:36,785
Group Two.

353
00:22:37,425 --> 00:22:40,505
Ms. Chen, I don't want to be with her!

354
00:22:41,225 --> 00:22:42,425
Ms. Chen.

355
00:22:43,185 --> 00:22:46,184
I am very happy to accept
your arrangement.

356
00:22:46,185 --> 00:22:47,744
As part of this class,

357
00:22:47,745 --> 00:22:50,265
I am willing to help

358
00:22:50,345 --> 00:22:51,704
someone physically underdeveloped

359
00:22:51,705 --> 00:22:53,624
and simple-minded students

360
00:22:53,625 --> 00:22:56,104
to step up with me
and defend the class' honor.

361
00:22:56,105 --> 00:22:57,135
That's good.

362
00:22:57,665 --> 00:23:00,535
Situ Feng, do you have any objections?

363
00:23:02,585 --> 00:23:03,865
No, ma'am.

364
00:23:05,025 --> 00:23:07,824
We're going to have a welcoming party
this weekend.

365
00:23:07,825 --> 00:23:10,184
Every class has to come out
with a program.

366
00:23:10,185 --> 00:23:11,955
Do you have any ideas?

367
00:23:12,025 --> 00:23:13,344
Situ Feng should sing!

368
00:23:13,345 --> 00:23:15,385
-Sing!
-Sing!

369
00:23:15,465 --> 00:23:18,064
This requires the approval
of those involved.

370
00:23:18,065 --> 00:23:20,935
Situ Feng, do you have any objections?

371
00:23:21,385 --> 00:23:22,225
No.

372
00:23:25,625 --> 00:23:26,544
Keep quiet now.

373
00:23:26,545 --> 00:23:28,144
Let's discuss the papers.

374
00:23:28,145 --> 00:23:29,944
Please refer to your papers.

375
00:23:29,945 --> 00:23:32,575
First, let's look at question two.

376
00:24:07,025 --> 00:24:10,024
<i>You were so pleased with yourself,
weren't you, Situ Feng?</i>

377
00:24:10,025 --> 00:24:16,775
<i>Now, let me show you what you get
when you cross Chen Qingqing.</i>

378
00:24:20,505 --> 00:24:21,624
Miss Chen Qingqing.

379
00:24:21,625 --> 00:24:24,424
-We're so sorry for what we did.
-Yeah.

380
00:24:24,425 --> 00:24:25,784
We didn't acknowledge you.

381
00:24:25,785 --> 00:24:30,024
-We didn't acknowledge you.
-Yes, if you could just forgive us.

382
00:24:30,025 --> 00:24:32,744
-We'll do anything to make it up to you.
-That's right.

383
00:24:32,745 --> 00:24:35,504
You just have to share with us
His Highness's latest news!

384
00:24:35,505 --> 00:24:38,325
Or you can just recommend us to him.

385
00:24:38,465 --> 00:24:42,064
We're so envious that you can be
by His Highness's side every day!

386
00:24:42,065 --> 00:24:46,585
That skin, those lips, that slender--

387
00:24:46,825 --> 00:24:48,145
Okay, stop it.

388
00:24:49,545 --> 00:24:51,825
I've told you before, right?

389
00:24:52,825 --> 00:24:54,105
The reason why

390
00:24:54,185 --> 00:24:57,344
they took pictures of me
with Situ Feng like that

391
00:24:57,345 --> 00:25:03,545
was because we seem to be
good friends in private.

392
00:25:03,625 --> 00:25:07,345
They didn't even care what sexes we are!

393
00:25:09,225 --> 00:25:10,425
Besides,

394
00:25:10,825 --> 00:25:13,015
for someone like Situ Feng...

395
00:25:13,025 --> 00:25:16,305
He's usually quite unmanly, you know?

396
00:25:20,705 --> 00:25:22,064
<i>Lucky for you.</i>

397
00:25:22,065 --> 00:25:25,104
Everyone is getting ready
for the welcoming party.

398
00:25:25,105 --> 00:25:27,264
We could use more hands here.

399
00:25:27,265 --> 00:25:29,664
So I've told the secretariat about it

400
00:25:29,665 --> 00:25:31,624
and they're willing to take you in.

401
00:25:31,625 --> 00:25:33,955
I'll surely get the job done!

402
00:25:35,945 --> 00:25:37,384
By the way, Mr. Gu.

403
00:25:37,385 --> 00:25:38,824
Can I ask you something?

404
00:25:38,825 --> 00:25:41,385
Which department is in charge

405
00:25:41,705 --> 00:25:43,525
of our college archives?

406
00:25:44,305 --> 00:25:47,344
Ming De's college archives are top secret.

407
00:25:47,345 --> 00:25:50,264
Only those in the presidium
can access them.

408
00:25:50,265 --> 00:25:52,275
Qingqing, why did you ask?

409
00:25:52,865 --> 00:25:55,985
Oh, it's nothing. I'm just curious.

410
00:25:56,705 --> 00:25:59,704
You've had a little misunderstanding
with someone in the council.

411
00:25:59,705 --> 00:26:02,464
You're just in time to clear the air.

412
00:26:02,465 --> 00:26:03,305
Come on.

413
00:26:10,505 --> 00:26:11,705
Chen Qingqing...

414
00:26:16,985 --> 00:26:18,185
Chen Qingqing...

415
00:26:27,585 --> 00:26:30,335
Chen Qingqing, you're right on time.

416
00:26:31,585 --> 00:26:33,225
It's you again?

417
00:26:48,065 --> 00:26:49,144
<i>I hope you don't mind.</i>

418
00:26:49,145 --> 00:26:53,144
<i>I don't blame you, but personal hygiene
is my highest priority.</i>

419
00:26:53,145 --> 00:26:55,264
<i>Aren't we studying math?
What are we doing here?</i>

420
00:26:55,265 --> 00:27:00,184
It's so peaceful and quiet here,
so it's the best place to study.

421
00:27:00,185 --> 00:27:04,165
<i>I wrote this song for her.</i>

422
00:27:06,545 --> 00:27:07,984
What the hell happened?

423
00:27:07,985 --> 00:27:08,984
Who's there?

424
00:27:08,985 --> 00:27:10,824
<i>Is something wrong with me?</i>

425
00:27:10,825 --> 00:27:13,624
<i>It's 120 beats per minute?</i>

426
00:27:13,625 --> 00:27:15,704
Isn't there anyone you like?

427
00:27:15,705 --> 00:27:18,525
I'm Chen Qingqing. Who would I like?

428
00:27:20,745 --> 00:27:22,995
Subtitle translation by CL Tan
